<p><date when="1803-09-25">Sept 25 1803</date></p>
<p>Dear Sir</p>

<p>I have sent the <persName>negar boy</persName> agreeabell to promise and you May Keep
him unto I send for him that is if he will sute you at 15 Dollars per
Month he is like the moust of negars you will have to mind him&#8212;</p>

<p><persName>Wm Reed</persName></p>
<p><persName>Capt M. Austen</persName></p>

        </div1>
